This Privacy Policy is a legal document between You (an individual who uses Luvmehair services) and Luvmehair.We know that You care how information about You is used and shared, and We appreciate Your trust that We will do so carefully and sensibly. This Privacy Policy describes how GUANGZHOU HETE TECHNOLOGY CO., LTD. and its affiliates (collectively “We,” “Us,” ,“Our”or “Luvme Hair”) collect and process Your personal information through Luvmehair websites and/or applications [Luvme Hair],devices, products, services, online and physical stores that reference this Privacy Policy (together "Luvmehair Services"). By using Luvmehair Services, You are consenting to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.
1.Collection of Personal Data
Personal data is information that can be used to directly or indirectly identify You. Personal data also includes anonymous data that is linked to information that can be used to directly or indirectly identify You. Personal data does not include data that has been irreversibly anonymized or aggregated so that it can no longer enable Us, whether in combination with other information or otherwise, to identify You.
