Additional State-Specific Privacy Disclosures
We use this Privacy Policy to make the disclosures required by state laws such as California Privacy Rights Act, Colorado Privacy Act, Connecticut Data Privacy Act, Utah Consumer Privacy Act, and Virginia Consumer Data Protection Act.
Note that the implementation details of some of these laws have not yet been finalized. We are always working to better comply with these laws and will update our processes, disclosures, and this notice as these implementing rules are finalized.
